race.comment: SEE YA LATER BABY (4) has been costly in two runs back but should be nearing his peak now. A more conservative ride may help him finish off. BLACK BUGATTI (1) never gave in fresh, arriving just in time to get the bob. Fitter for that and worth sticking with. TRANTORO (9) is hard to catch but his best is good enough. Drawn well and worth keeping safe. RAYMOND'S REWARD (2) put in a much better performance last start and should be right at his peak now third up. Drawn well and shapes as one of the main chances. REVOLUTION BELLE (10) was only narrowly beaten last start, next best.
